Good work.
Here, some refreshments.
Ah, thanks.

I brought a variety
so drink whatever you want.

...Hey, which one do you think
Fuyu wants to drink?

Eh?
I mean, whichever ones you like...

Oh dear. Who was it again that said they would
properly do their research on Fuyu?

Or perhaps... Has Fuyu's producer already completely
lost interest in Fuyu?
